{"tid":902800,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【零售市道復蘇】銅鑼灣羅素街舖租貴絕全球","createTime":"2018-11-15T05:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T07:14:06.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1cca1cc0c1481deb45120077fdea189ae16bbd4b","tid":902800,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T05:22:59.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】本港零售市道復蘇，商舖價格及租金亦有所回升。有物業顧問報告指，銅鑼灣羅素街舖租今年重奪榜首。<br />\n戴德梁行報告指，今年第二季銅鑼灣羅素街舖租繼2013年後，再度成為全球最昂貴商業街道，每年每平方呎租金為2671美元，折合近2.1萬港元，按年下跌1.5%，但排名仍由去年第二位，攀升至今年第一位。<br />\n羅素街舖租較排第二的紐約第五大道上段高約18%，至於第三位排名與去年一樣，是倫敦新邦德街。<br />\n有關報告自1988年發表，統計全球65個國家、446條主要商業街道。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=327267&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D327267%26refer%3D&d=ZWcZKNvS28CkH%2Fe%2BhxUukEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0176d20e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D327267%26refer%3D&h=6a4e175f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=327267&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\nHONG KONG NO.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921ab15ed53b5ac5b9f01ca86697738c63e6fb54","tid":902800,"uid":118623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"無知一問 嗰間成人玩具店究竟係點做"},{"pid":"20e7adb69ca0616474a7c902c433001d5875ecb3","tid":902800,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"921ab15ed53b5ac5b9f01ca86697738c63e6fb54","tid":902800,"uid":118623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"無知一問 嗰間成人玩具店究竟係點做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T05:30:48.000Z","msg":"嗰度多上流社會先容易多生意"},{"pid":"8237564617b547c33f7d5efee6c42afcd7903185","tid":902800,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"921ab15ed53b5ac5b9f01ca86697738c63e